{"id":616275,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/【立此存照】小米知错就改/","date":"2019-08-27T18:37:53Z","modified":"2019-08-27T18:37:53Z","title":"【立此存照】小米知错就改","content":"<p>CDT 编者按：@Redmi红米电视 在微博发布Redmi电视广告内容：“五大平台，缺一不可”。@环球网 转发并评论“缺脑如此，无药可救”。很快，@@Redmi红米电视将广告内容改为“海量内容”。@环球网转发并评论：“知错就改，加强学习。”网民留言，原因在于“五大平台，缺一不可” 完美呼应了香港的“五大诉求，缺一不可”。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-616276\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1-38.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"365\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1-38.jpg 1125w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1-38-300x219.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1-38-768x560.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1-38-1024x747.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-616277\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/2-21.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"830\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/2-21.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/2-21-181x300.jpg 181w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/2-21-768x1274.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/2-21-617x1024.jpg 617w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"st-related-posts\">\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2019.07.22</span> <a title=\"【异闻观止】网友发诋毁伊春市形象“打油诗” 4人被拘\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/07/%e3%80%90%e5%bc%82%e9%97%bb%e8%a7%82%e6%ad%a2%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e5%8f%8b%e5%8f%91%e8%af%8b%e6%af%81%e4%bc%8a%e6%98%a5%e5%b8%82%e5%bd%a2%e8%b1%a1%e6%89%93%e6%b2%b9%e8%af%97-4%e4%ba%ba/\">【异闻观止】网友发诋毁伊春市形象“打油诗” 4人被拘</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2019.06.28</span> <a title=\"唐一水：大阉割时代已经来临\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/06/%e5%94%90%e4%b8%80%e6%b0%b4%ef%bc%9a%e5%a4%a7%